<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Best Scrabble Words With V — Strategy & High Scorers</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">V is Scrabble's most awkward 4-point tile. While H and Y pair flexibly with consonants, V almost always demands a vowel next to it and refuses to sit at the end of words. Smart players know V words by heart so they can dump it quickly without sacrificing points. Learn these patterns and V becomes an asset, not a liability.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">V Tile at a Glance</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">4 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Tile value</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">2</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Tiles in bag</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">Vowel hungry</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Almost always needs A/E/I/O</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

