  <p class="text-base text-gray-200">Most English words don't end in V, but Scrabble has valid exceptions. Memorise these <span class="text-white font-medium">V-ending words</span> for when V lands at the end of your play: REV, DEV, GOV, LUV, TAV, LAV, GAV, NAV, SAV, VIV, SPIV, PERV.</p>
